{"tid":2131602,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多謝許智勇開放辦事處，好等我可以有尊嚴食飯","createTime":"2020-07-30T03:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T03:09:47.000Z","uid":123488,"like":69,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b05fa12fed7c8eb765483b1a44fae1be8bacf684","tid":2131602,"uid":123488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ERT5HrC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FERT5HrC.jpg&h=6b18405a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華X盤到琴日開始捉得好緊<br />\n唔比人地盤內人聚集多人食飯<br />\n有公園，但附近豪宅保安趕我地走，話影響市容<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返到去加上落雨，樓面好多白帽趕師傅走<br />\n唯有上高空set位食飯<br />\n<br />\n又驚上面棚落石屎仔加餸，一聽到上面有聲就收埋盒飯<br />\n琴日果餐，食得最唔安落，驚住食<br />\n雖然做藍領命苦，但唔想咁命賤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得知今日許智勇辦事處開放食飯<br />\n可能有人話我係打手，話我係PR<br />\n但唔駛諗去邊落腳，可以涼陣冷氣<br />\n出面34度，烈日當空，長期散唔到熱<br />\n我求咩姐？我求食飯可以坐係張櫈喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望可以比d支持，難得有議員關注藍領/基層<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9jMCyAx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9jMCyAx.jpg&h=39f44997&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3939b3dfb46d4e69aa99aa54c4d8f98d59fe8f7","tid":2131602,"uid":224848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ede4ea7af34a21a018b5e3e585cb89ead07e7be","tid":2131602,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efd146f8d57d60732b11f0dec7bce8d78215ab1","tid":2131602,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5eadb27ec13695096a4b62a3c4aefc1b4ab2b0","tid":2131602,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:58:20.000Z"